### Get All Packages (No filters)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/packages

###

### Get Packages with Pagination
GET http://localhost:3000/api/packages?page=1&limit=5

###

### Get Single Package by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/packages/package_123

###

### Get Package Activities
GET http://localhost:3000/api/packages/package_123/activities

###

### Get Package Media
GET http://localhost:3000/api/packages/package_123/media

###

### Create New Package (Admin only)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/packages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Adventure Package",
  "description": "An exciting adventure package with multiple activities",
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/package.jpg",
  "isCustom": false,
  "basePrice": 500
}

###

### Update Package (Admin only)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/packages/package_123
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Adventure Package",
  "basePrice": 550
}

###

### Add Activity to Package (Admin only)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/packages/package_123/activities
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "activityId": "activity_456"
}

###

### Remove Activity from Package (Admin only)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/packages/package_123/activities/activity_456

###

### Upload Package Media (Admin only)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/packages/package_123/media
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "media": [
    {
      "mediaUrl": "https://example.com/image1.jpg",
      "mediaType": "image",
      "altText": "Package main image",
      "displayOrder": 0
    },
    {
      "mediaUrl": "https://example.com/video1.mp4",
      "mediaType": "video",
      "altText": "Package intro video",
      "displayOrder": 1
    }
  ]
}

###

### Delete Package Media (Admin only)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/packages/package_123/media/media_789

###

### Delete Package (Admin only)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/packages/package_123
